caption.p: Neutralizing antibody titers following PIZV vaccination and ZIKV challenge. Rhesus macaques were vaccinated on days 1 and 29 and challenged on day 71. Individual Zika RVP titers for each vaccine group on study day 1 (prior to vaccination), day 29 (28 days post-first dose), day 57 (28 days post-second dose), day 71 (prior to ZIKV challenge), and day 101 (30 days post-ZIKV challenge). Mean and standard deviation are shown for all groups and time points.
